entries.journal_entry_description: You're doing some entertainer work for Gendra.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Go to the cantina and perform.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Gendra has asked you to fill in for a dancer who can't make their performance at the local cantina. Head to the cantina and go inside. Give a 30 second performance, and then return back to Gendra.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: You've finished dancing at the cantina. Go see Gendra.
